snippet.description:

Khumar Episode 01 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 24th November 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

snippet.title: 40 दिन सर्दी में 3 चम्मच खाकर देखिये हड्डीयों की कट-कट, माइग्रेन, अनिद्रा, जोड़ो में दर्द कभी नहीहोगा
snippet.description:
#winterrecipebyeatyammiecious  
#energybooster #dryfruits 


Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*Ingredients for gond dry fruit paak :-

1/4cup - Edible Gum
1 cup - Lotus Seeds
1/2cup - Almonds
1/2cup - Cashews
1/2cup - Walnut
1/2cup - Dry Coconut
1tbs - Dry Ginger Powder
1tbs - White Pepper Powder
1ts - Green Cardamom Powder
1/4ts - Nutmeg
1/2cup - Jaggery
3tbs - Clarified Butter
2 cup - Milk
(If you want you can add dry dates instead of jaggery Watch this recipe - https://youtu.be/bmHbihdn9Cg?si=rot8djUqSlKySvaR )

snippet.title: Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - 25th November 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Khumar Episode 02 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 25th November 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz

छठ पूजा | Episode 03 - Melodies of India 

The Mahaparv of Bihar is here and I wanted to witness it since a very long time. So this time I just booked my tickets in advance and reached the infamous gun capital of Bihar, Munger. To experience Chhatt Puja like a local with native people of the land

Chhatti Maiyaa ki jai 🙏🏼
==========================================================

Heading onto a new journey, that's shape me inside out :) 

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3938 | 25 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3938: Jethalal Ke Khilaaf Complaint
--------------------------------------------------------
 Champaklal and the other men from Gokuldham are shocked by Pandey's evidence. Although Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka admit that their voices are on the tapes, they never meant to threaten a lady.
 Members of the Gokuldham Society show up at the police station in an attempt to persuade Inspector Panday to release Jethalal. Will they be heard by Inspector Panday? Watch the episode

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3938, 25 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3937 | 24 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3937: ACP Ki Biwi Ko Di Dhamki
--------------------------------------------------------
Chalu Pandey informs Jetha that a complaint has been filed against him by an Ahmedabad resident. Jagruti is the wife of a well-known cop who has been threatened by Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka. Chalu Pandey plays voice recordings of Jetha and Bagha speaking badly. Champaklal and the other Gokuldham men are taken aback by Pandey's proof. Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka acknowledge that the tapes contain their voices, but they had no intention of threatening a woman. So, how are they going to prove their innocence?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3937, 24 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 1525: വൃക്ക തകരിലാക്കുന്ന ജ്യുസ് | Juice which causes kidney failure
snippet.description:
1525: വൃക്ക തകരിലാക്കുന്ന ജ്യുസ് | Juice which causes kidney failure

പ്രകൃതിദത്തമായത് എന്ന ഒരു വാക്ക് കേട്ടാല്‍ ഏതു സാധനവും എത്ര വേണമെങ്കിലും കഴിക്കാം എന്ന ചിന്തയാണ് ഇന്നത്തെ സമൂഹത്തിനുള്ളത്. കാരണം പ്രകൃതിയില്‍ നിന്നുള്ള എല്ലാം വിഷവിമുക്തമാണെന്നു കണ്ണുമടച്ച്‌ വിശ്വസിക്കുന്നവരാണ് നമ്മളിൽ പലരും.

പ്രകൃതിയില്‍ നിന്നു കിട്ടുന്ന എല്ലാ വസ്തുക്കളും അളവില്ലാതെ കഴിക്കുന്നത് അത്ര നല്ല രീതിയല്ല. വ്യാജ വൈദ്യന്മാരും യൂട്യൂബിൽ വണ്ണം കുറയ്ക്കാനും ഷുഗർ, കൊളെസ്ട്രോൾ, രക്തസമ്മർദ്ദം കുറയ്ക്കാനും പല സാധനങ്ങളും കൊള്ളാമെന്നു തരത്തിൽ പല മെസ്സേജുകളും ഇറക്കുന്നുണ്ട്. സത്യത്തില്‍ പ്രകൃതിയില്‍ നിന്നു ലഭിക്കുന്നവയെല്ലാം അളവ് നോക്കാതെ കഴിക്കാമോ? അത്തരത്തിൽ ഉള്ള ഒരു ജ്യൂസ്‌ ആണ് നിങ്ങൾ അറിഞ്ഞിരിക്കേണ്ടത്. കിഡ്നി തകരാർ ഉണ്ടാക്കുന്ന ഈ ജ്യൂസ് ഒഴിവാക്കുക. ഇത് എന്ത്‌ കൊണ്ടാണ് ഇങ്ങനെ സംഭവിക്കുന്നത് എന്ന് മനസിലാക്കി മറ്റുള്ളവർക്കായി ഈ വീഡിയോ ഷെയർ ചെയ്യുക.

#drdanishsalim #ddbl #danishsalim #drdbetterlife #juice_danger #natural_juice #വണ്ണം_കുറയ്ക്കാൻ_ജ്യൂസ്‌ #പ്രമേഹം_കുറയ്ക്കാൻ_ജ്യുസ് #കൊളെസ്ട്രോൾ_കുറയ്ക്കാൻ_ജ്യുസ് #ജ്യൂസ്‌_കുടിച്ചു_വൃക്ക_തകരാർ

*****Dr. Danish Salim*****

Dr Danish Salim; currently working as Specialist Emergency Department, Sheikh Khalifa Medical City, Abu Dubai, UAE Health Authority & Managing Director at Dr D Better Life Pvt Ltd. He was the academic director and head of the emergency department at PRS Hospital, Kerala. He has over 10 years of experience in emergency and critical care. He was awarded the SEHA Hero award and is one of the first doctors to receive a Golden Visa from the UAE Government for his contributions to Health Care.

He was active in the field of emergency medicine and have
contributed in bringing in multiple innovations for which Dr
Danish was awarded nationally as "Best innovator in emergency medicine and young achiever" as well as the “Best emergency physician of state award".

Among multiple innovations like app for accident alerts, jump kits for common emergency management, Dr Danish brought into being the state's first bike ambulance with KED and a single state wide-app to control and coordinate private and public ambulances under one platform with the help of Indian Medical Association and Kerala Police. This network was appreciated and is successfully running with the support of the government of Kerala currently.

Besides the technology field, Dr Danish was enthusiastic in conducting more than 2000 structured emergency training classes for common men, residents, doctors and healthcare professionals over the span of 5 years.

Positions Held

1. Kerala state Secretary: Society for Emergency Medicine India

2. National Innovation Head Society for Emergency Medicine India

3. Vice President Indian Medical Association Kovalam

snippet.title: बंगाल के खाड़ी में बन सकता है तूफान मिगजौम राजस्थान, गुजरात एमपी और महाराष्ट्र में मूसलाधार बारिश
snippet.description:
बंगाल की खाड़ी में समुद्री तूफान बनने वाला है इसका कई राज्यों पर असर होगा। पहाड़ों पर नया वेस्टर्न डिस्टरबेंस। 26 नवंबर को कई राज्यों में मूसलाधार बारिश का कर दिखाई देगा। राजस्थान के कुछ जिलों सहित महाराष्ट्र गुजरात तथा दक्षिण पश्चिम मध्य प्रदेश में भारी बारिश की संभावना है अंडमान और निकोबार दीप समूह में भी तेज बारिश के साथ तेज हवाएं चलेंगी। दिल्ली में वायु गुणवत्ता खतरनाक श्रेणी में रहेगी।

snippet.description:
"Shayarana" by Kayden Sharma seamlessly merges Shayari (poetry) with Hip-Hop, creating a captivating and melodious track with love as its central theme. 

Credits 
Track Name: Shayarana
Written & Performed By: @kaydensharma 
Music Producer: @anuragsaikia6277 
Co-Composer: Kayden Sharma, Oblong Sioni, Ankur Jyoti

Music Label: @tseries 

Genre: Hip Hop

Sub-Genre: Rap

Language: Hindi

Country Of Origin/Source: India

Mix and Mastered by: Hanish Taneja (Studio Alika)

ANDAZ TERA KHOOBSURAT BESABAR YE ROOH MERI
TADAPTA RAATON MEIN TAB TU EK LAUTI SUKOON MERI
KAL KU BADA MAHAL BANAKE KHUD ICH USME KHO GAYA TOH
TU ICH HAI WOH JO UDHAR BHI MEKU DHOOND LETI

IMAARAT YEH LADKA TERA PYAAR USKI EENTE
NEEND MEIN BHI MEKU TERI KHUSHBOO ROZ KHEENCHE
YEH SHAYAR KI SHAYARI KE ALAG HAI TAREEKE 
RHYME AATI NAHI NAZAR MEIN PHIR BHI FANAA HOTI INPE

KARUN TERI TAREEFAAN TOH KABHI KHATAM NAHI HOTI
TERE PE LIKHNE AAYA TOH PHIR GHAZAL BHI PAD JAATI CHHOTI
MERI YE RAGON MEIN TU DAUD TI NASHA BANKE
JAB MAIN HOTA CHOKE TU AAJATI HAWA BANKE

BANKE REHNA CHAHTA MAIN TERI SAREE KA FALL
RAPPER HOON ISLIYE BOHOT BOLTU LEKIN TERE AAGE MOUN
TU NAHI MADHURI NA MAIN SALMAN PHIR KYON AATA YEH SAWAL
KI HUM AAPKE HAIN KOUN

SABH RAKHTI MERE PE DHYAAN PAR TU RAKHTI MERA DHYAAN 
KAISE SAMJHAOUN KI MAIN KITNA PYAAR KARTA TERE SE
ITTEFAQ HAI KI LADKI HAI TU WARNA LADKA BHI HOTI TOH UTTA ICH PYAAR KARTA TERE SE

HOTA NAHI LIMIT MEIN
DUNIYA GHUMNA CHAHTA MAIN EK NAHI DO TICKET PE
DEKH KE TERI SAADGI KALAM NAHI RUKI TOH
TERE CHARITRA KE CHITRA KO MAIN BAYAAN KARRA LIKHIT MEIN

ADA WOH TERI UFF HAAYE RAMA
MERI RANI TU SHEHER KA MAIN BADSHAH                                         
HIP HOP KAROON WOH BHI SHAYARANA
SEEDHE MAUT DAALU MEHFIL MEIN POORE BOLTE WAH WAH

AB TU ICH BOL KI MAIN KHUDKU KAISA CHHOD SAKTA
YOU KNOW TEKU DEKH KE KAISA LAGTA MEKU 
J CHHORD SHABDON MEIN NAHI BOL SAKTA

POORI ZINDAGI TERE SATH REH SAKTA BINA TEKU CHHUE
TRUST ME WHEN I SAY KI MERA HEART PURE HAI 
UPAR SE MERI KUNDALI MEIN RAJYOG HAI

TERE CHEHRE PE HAI SAADGI NIGAHON MEIN SHARARATI
ZULFON MEIN ULJHAN AUR PAYAL KARTI CHHAN CHHAN 
KAALI KURTI PE WOH LAAL CHUNI DAALKE JAB CHALTI
TERE KADMO KE SAATH CHALTI DHADKAN

JANNAT SE KAM NAHI JI HASSI TERE CHEHRE PE 
ZINDA HOON ABHI TAK KYONKI ROZ MARTA TERE PE
EHSAAN KARKE GINTI NAHI WILD HAI PAR CHINDI NAHI
THAKURAINE HAI TU AADESH KAR VINTI NAHI

PATNI MERI BANKE JAB AAYENGI TU GHAR PE 
YEH HOTA JABH MAIN WAPAS AATA DUNIYA BADAL KE
DAAYAN HAATH REHTA MERA EK DIN FALAK PE
PAR BAAYAN HAATH REHTA TERE HAATH KO PAKAD KE

ISSHAARE TUMHARE SAMAJH NAHI AA RAHE
BHULARE BHULARE
LINE BHUL GAYA RE
CHHUTA RE CHHUTA RE
LINE CHHUT GAYA RE
PAR TERE NASHE MEIN KHUCHH BHI GUNGUNA RE

snippet.title: PM Modi Meets the Men in Blue, Comforts Indian Cricket Team After World Cup Final
snippet.description:
PM Narendra Modi meets Indian Cricket Team | Prime Minister Narendra Modi visited Team India dressing room after the India vs Australia final World Cup match in Ahmedabad and comforted the team after their defeat in the game. The PM was seen motivating Rohit Sharma, Virat Kohli, Ravindra Jadeja, Mohammad Shami, Jasprit Bumrah as well as other players. He applauded coach Rahul Dravid and praised the entire team for the efforts. The PM also extended an invitation to the entire team to meet in Delhi.

snippet.title: Dil Dosti Dating | EP 2 | Fight Over Female Flatmate | Hasley India
snippet.description:
The new girl has entered the house and Naman can hear the silence before the storm. Naman ko lagta hai that there is something fishy about Harsha lekin Paras hogya hai pyaar Mei andha!

And what would be better than a flatmate jisko khana banana bhi aata ho aur baat karna bhi!
Toh bas ab Naman aur Paras ki dosti ke beech aa chuki hai ek ladki!

Will Paras and Naman be able to save their bond? 
Kya Harsha ke shift hone peeche chupa hai koi raaz?

Jaanne ke liye episode ko end tak zarur dekhna!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 100: Reyansh's Token Of Love 
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Malini arrives in Delhi in order to keep an eye on what Reyansh will do with Aradhana's wedding and whether he will not disrupt all the planned functions. Now, Stay Tuned what exciting games will Reyansh play in order to win Aradhana back in her life, and also Jai plans to bring her mother in order to let her meet Aradhana. 

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka
Cast: Shivangi Joshi, Kushal Tandon, Nausheen Ali Sardar, Simba Nagpal
Episode: 100
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

#barsateinmausampyaarka #setindia #बरसातेंमौसमप्यारका #kushaltandon #shivangijoshi 

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

snippet.title: मेथी ना खाने वाले भी रोज़ किलो किलो मेथी ख़रीदेंगे मेथी का ये नाश्ता खाकर Healthy Hari Methi Recipe
snippet.description:
मेथी ना खाने वाले भी रोज़ किलो किलो मेथी ख़रीदेंगे मेथी का ये नाश्ता खाकर Healthy Hari Methi Recipe

#HariMethiKaNashta#Cutlet#NirmlaNehraRecipes

Ingredients:-
Fenugreek Leaves-300 gm
Gram Flour-1 cup
Flattened Rice-1/2 cup
Ginger-1 inch piece 
Garlic Cloves-5-6
Green Chilli-2-3
Coriander Seeds-2 tsp
Fennel Seeds-1 tsp
Cumin Seeds-1 tsp
Sesame Seeds-2-3 tbsp
Red Chili Powder-1 tsp 
Turmeric Powder-1/2 tsp
Coriander Leaves 
Salt-to taste
Oil-for frying

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi

snippet.title: How Napoleon Conquered Europe? | Was he a Hero or Villain? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
This video by Dhruv Rathee explores the fascinating life of Napoleon Bonaparte, a figure who evokes mixed opinions. Born in Corsica shortly after it fell under French control, Napoleon's journey from a young boy influenced by Enlightenment thinkers to a powerful military and political leader is captivating. Despite being mocked for his Corsican roots, he excelled in military school and quickly rose through the ranks. His role during the French Revolution and subsequent rise to power, including his self-coronation as Emperor, showcases his complex character. The video delves into his administrative reforms, like the Napoleonic Code, and his conquests across Europe. However, it also critically examines the darker aspects of his reign, including the reintroduction of slavery and his ultimate decline, marked by failed campaigns and eventual exile.  

Link to the videos mentioned - 
The Untold Mystery of Indus Valley Civilization | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/Lr7GMr1NzV0?si=vLl3az4SPB8S-G40
French Revolution | Why it happened? | The Dark Reality | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/pGzmmjDDHJg?si=B-uNGivWT5LP6wJU

localized.title: How Napoleon Conquered Europe? | Was he a Hero or Villain? | Dhruv Rathee
localized.description:
This video by Dhruv Rathee explores the fascinating life of Napoleon Bonaparte, a figure who evokes mixed opinions. Born in Corsica shortly after it fell under French control, Napoleon's journey from a young boy influenced by Enlightenment thinkers to a powerful military and political leader is captivating. Despite being mocked for his Corsican roots, he excelled in military school and quickly rose through the ranks. His role during the French Revolution and subsequent rise to power, including his self-coronation as Emperor, showcases his complex character. The video delves into his administrative reforms, like the Napoleonic Code, and his conquests across Europe. However, it also critically examines the darker aspects of his reign, including the reintroduction of slavery and his ultimate decline, marked by failed campaigns and eventual exile.

About the Channel:

आज वक़्त के जिस दौर में हम जी रहे हैं उसमें आने वाला पल किस शक्ल में हमारे सामने आएगा कोई नहीं जानता। हां....अगर हम कुछ कर सकते हैं तो सिर्फ़ इतना कि आने वाले पल के क़दमों की आहट को ज़रूर भांप सकते हैं। मगर आने वाले वक़्त की नीयत क्या है ये तभी जाना जा सकता है जब हम अपने आंख और कान खुले रखें। और इसमें CRIME TAK आपकी मदद करेगा। क्राइम की दुनिया की हर छोटी-बड़ी ख़बरों से आपको आगाह करके। ताकि आप सुरक्षित रहें।

Nowadays we are living in such a age, where one knows that what will happen in next moment? In such scenario what we can do is to be stay aware each moment. We can prepare for future only if we keep our eyes and ears open. CRIME TAK is here to help and assist you in this regard, by making you aware of all crime related incidents/stories, so that you can be safe.
